cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a novel end-to-end trainable embedding model based on deep metric learning. The paper also involves the use of deep neural networks and distance metrics, which are common topics in machine learning research. 

It could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the proposed method involves embedding sequences of text data. 

Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the proposed method could be applied to image data. 

cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are also possible sub-categories as the paper involves the use of deep neural networks and machine learning techniques.
